credited investor, you can get in on the action with Percent [ https://subs=
tack.com/redirect/372e10a6-f26c-4ff3-9bbd-1509805a90a6?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3Qi=
fQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ].
